title: Gabriel Iglesias Presents Stand Up Revolution Season 720p HDTV
description: Gabriel Iglesias is a comedian of many words. Now with his new show "Gabriel Iglesias Presents Stand-Up Revolution", he finally gets to have his friends and Ozomatli, the house band, provide laughs for all to share in. Airing on Comedy Central, the show will be 30 minutes of stand-up comedy that will feature a wide variety of comedians who have a joke to tell. Come along and join Fluffy and friends on a comedy party that you will enjoy!
